<p style="margin-bottom: 21px; text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin-top: 5px;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;">各学院、各部门、广大校友：</span><br/></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">二</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">秩芳华，桃李天下。在</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">即将迎来</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">二</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">十华诞之际，为彰显学校办学成果，展示优秀校友在各领域的突出成就、先进事迹和绚丽风采，激励更多学子奋发进取、成长成才，激励在校师生不忘初心、砥砺前行。现面向各学院、各</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">部门、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">广大校友征集在各行各业取得优秀成绩、做出突出贡献的校友事迹材料。现决定开展优秀校友信息征集工作，具体事宜通知如下：</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">一、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">征集对象</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">建校</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">0年以来毕业的历届校友</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">二、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">推荐条件</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">在各自领域、行业中业绩突出，为所在地方社会发展作出突出贡献，为母校赢得荣誉的优秀校友。优秀校友范畴包括但不局限以下范围：</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">在国家、省市党政机关、企事业单位（曾）担任重要职务者；</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">企业高管，自主创业取得突出成就者；</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">知名教授、专家学者、技能大师或在本职工作领域中有突出贡献者；</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">主持重大工程或重大科研项目，并取得重大成就者；</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">5．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">参与国家重大工程建设、重大战略科研项目者；</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">6．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">获省市级以上荣誉称号、奖励者；</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">7．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">扎根基层，默默奉献，支援国家建设，取得突出成绩的基层工作者；</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">8．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">热心公益事业，为社会做出特殊贡献者；</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">、</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">9．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">社会知名人士；</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">10．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">关心母校发展，为学校发展捐资助学或设立奖学金者；</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">11．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">在其它领域表现突出者。</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">三、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">材料征集方式</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">请各学院</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">部门</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">收集优秀校友事迹，汇总后提交至指定邮箱。</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">欢迎广大校友直接向学校推荐或自荐。</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">四、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">征集内容</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">个人简历：主要内容为姓名、性别、出生年月、毕业时间、专业、工作单位、职务职称、主要著述或成就、获奖情况等</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">事迹材料：主要内容为奋斗经历、创业历程、工作业绩等，字数不少于</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">800字。事迹材料力求思路清晰，事迹要典型、真实，语言简练，涉及到数字的要准确、具体。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">照片资料：电子版人物照片</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2-3张（标准照、工作照、生活照均可）、获奖证书。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">媒体报道：如有省、市级以上媒体对校友个人相关报道，请提供媒体链接、报道时间、报道截图、报道全文等材料。</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">五、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">征集要求</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">征集时间：优秀校友信息收集工作长期持续开展，首批征集时间截止</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">10</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">月</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">30日。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2．</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">各学院、各</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">部门</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">和自我推荐的校友可将事迹材料、照片资料命名为</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">“优秀校友事迹+姓名”发送至邮箱：</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">804532064qq.com</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">六、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">联系方式</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">联系人：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">徐元斌</span> &nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">联系电话：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">15727675163</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">七、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">附件</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 黑体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 21px">附件一：江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style="font-family: 黑体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 21px">优秀校友推荐表</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 黑体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 黑体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:336px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:336px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友联络办公室</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:336px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">202</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">9</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">27</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">日</span></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;" src="/resource/js/ueditor-1.4.3.3/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif"/><a style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/data/upload/img/20231010/1696920226970043213.docx" title="江西软件职业技术大学优秀校友推荐表.docx">江西软件职业技术大学优秀校友推荐表.docx</a></p>